{"tid":2173640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"在香港, 做女仔好易生存","createTime":"2020-08-25T11:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T04:33:50.000Z","uid":272077,"like":55,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe934774f8e41c715458ac6edde1a380b719c11","tid":2173640,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係指生存, 唔好話乜野豬扒都好難有人要(7頭都好難有人要吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? )<br />\n<br />\n生得靚果d, 大把人追<br />\n好身材果d, 又大把人追<br />\n後生果d, 樣普普通通, 都大把追<br />\n大把著數<br />\n<br />\n番工, 隨便找份sales, 隨便的月入過15k, 但sales幾時會請男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然, 可以釣個有錢人, 那怕你出身公屋, 甚至劏房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做文職, 被認為細心, 有耐性又優先<br />\n想上位, 找生意, 做主角/大配角, 同人上幾次房就得啦. 男仔就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我說得對嗎, 有沒有偏見先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613259655ddde6ea3260e1ccbffa8266ecfb9ab7","tid":2173640,"uid":370297,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:08:29.000Z","msg":"仔都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894dc49c3938fbb3d55f4b563fad78768ed3d312","tid":2173640,"uid":81737,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"廢就廢啦"},{"pid":"b334c33d9fe088fe44d4f5cf3d856107804851e7","tid":2173640,"uid":262863,"like":5,"dislike":12,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:31:39.000Z","msg":"女仔先難生存"},{"pid":"ededd9274612ed2f6d5d3543816d60056fa0882d","tid":2173640,"uid":249170,"like":26,"dislike":7,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:34:11.000Z","msg":"就算香港女仔生活好過男仔，都係班弱雞港男賦予比佢地<br />\n其實講真果句，香港根本唔係女權社會<br />\n係 男奴社會<br />\n<br />\n成班弱雞港男對女不對事<br />\n發輝大愛精神討好條女，乜都聽條女話<br />\n<br />\n最簡單<br />\n女性係會幫女性<br />\n但男性會幫女性攻擊男性<